# ─── Firebase / config secrets ───
.firebase/
firebase-debug.log*
firestore-debug.log*
ui-debug.log*
serviceAccountKey*.json
# NOTE: firebase_options.dart IS committed. Its values are client config that
# ship in the app binary (not secrets); security is enforced by Firestore rules
# + App Check. The native google-services.json / GoogleService-Info.plist below
# are ignored only because the native folders are generated locally.

